Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveAmerican actress and director, Tasha Smith, has only praises for the Nigerian fashion scene after attending Saturday’s Africa Magic Viewer’s Choice Awards in Lagos.
The actress and her twin sister, Sidra, went live on Instagram at the event.
Sidra started off by saying, “Nigeria is not playing with fashion. These women are out here slaying.”Continuing, Tasha said, “They be beating their faces honey and the clothes. And the men, they dress! The clothes are incredible, the fashion is incredible, the talent is incredible. I want all of my brothers and sisters out there in America to make sure, you get a chance to visit Nigeria.”
She added that she and her twin had traced their ancestry and found they were 46 per cent Nigerian.
